Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.09,0:02:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.62,0:02:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里已经没有我们的家了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:11.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无形境界线什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.34,0:02:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无形境界线是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.07,0:02:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.40,0:04:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为十花小姐说得很对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.50,0:04:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我想正是因为明白这一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是因为明白这一点  六花才会这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算别人说「这就是现实  你必须接受」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是会有许多无法承受的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  一波未平一波又起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.75,0:04:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没来得及整理自己的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.69,0:04:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切就都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在逃避  也不打算忽视
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:36.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是以这种理所当然的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.89,0:04:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受这些所谓理所当然的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.14,0:04:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样真的没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.79,0:04:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  大家都说这是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说现实就是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就真的没有问题了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是现实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.26,0:04:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都是这样活着的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.49,0:04:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓的成长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.37,0:05:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.35,0:05:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.92,0:05:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.24,0:05:23.24,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fad(0,500)\pos(95,386)}第八集{\fs32}{\alpha&HFF}\Naaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa{\alpha}E   x   i   l   e\N{\fs0}两个人的…  逃避之行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.88,0:05:31.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  六花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才坐出租车回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过大概又去海边了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她回来前  大家都去海边放烟花了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:05:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于到了解放暗黑龙的时刻了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.46,0:06:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.55,0:06:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来来  要扔了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.55,0:06:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我丢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个好有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  富樫君和六花好慢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.61,0:06:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.04,0:06:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假来到海边  两人再悄悄出门
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.31,0:06:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是去邂逅平行世界的战士了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  富樫君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.72,0:06:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六花呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她没来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.39,0:07:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富樫君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.41,0:07:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是青春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说是修罗场
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修罗场是强力的结界魔法…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  还好赶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.22,0:07:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我要说的话  你打算去哪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个地方  管理局的势力实在太大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结界的力量太强了  只能撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说要回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太是从哪里获得了黑暗火焰的力量呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了那些东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.51,0:08:24.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始也就只是朋友之间说说而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然大家都说一起出去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我是例外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.23,0:08:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得自己有点不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.72,0:08:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟他们之间有一种违和感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.33,0:08:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说是一种脱离于世界般的  奇妙的孤独感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是黑暗意识唤醒了其他世界的记忆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.02,0:08:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎也有过这种感觉  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.37,0:08:54.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想忘掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  是管理局的干扰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:08:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.19,0:09:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.33,0:09:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,视线对上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来  我们就缔结了更高一级的契约
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.46,0:09:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑炎掌控者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.34,0:09:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你便了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.85,0:09:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在黑暗火焰的怀抱中…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.67,0:09:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别玩了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.99,0:08:06.12,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}誰が気付けただろう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:13.24,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}光の向こうで　濃くなる影に
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:19.16,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}過去が遠くで叫んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:25.10,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}背中向ければ　耳を塞いでる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:31.43,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}辛くからって　弱いと決めないで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:37.72,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}泣かないからって　強いと思わないで
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:44.00,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君が握る手　温かさを
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:50.02,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}信じてみてもいいかな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:56.96,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}やっと気付いた　ようやく見つけた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:09:03.11,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}涙でぼやけた真実
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:09.31,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}僕は僕でいいと　頭を撫でながら
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.80,0:09:15.78,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}眠る君の横顔が今
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:22.64,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}新しい気持ちを照らした
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:27.54,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ありがとう　そばにいてくれて
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:35.28,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}芽吹いたよ　始まりの種が
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.99,0:08:06.12,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是否有人会察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:13.24,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在光明的另一端  渐渐清晰的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.67,0:08:19.16,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}过去在远方呼喊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.79,0:08:25.10,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}转过身去  充耳不听
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.06,0:08:31.43,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不要因为痛苦  就否定我的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:37.72,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}虽然我不流泪  但不意味着坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:44.00,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你紧握的手  传来的温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:50.02,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是否可以依靠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.02,0:08:56.96,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}终于察觉  终于发现
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:09:03.11,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}被泪水模糊的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.56,0:09:09.31,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你轻抚着我的头  让我勇敢做自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.80,0:09:15.78,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}此时此刻  你的睡颜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:22.64,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}照亮了我崭新的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.44,0:09:27.54,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}感谢你能陪伴在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:35.28,INC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}新生的种子  已经发芽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.53,0:09:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是富樫君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.63,0:09:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说小鸟游同学要回家  所以去送她了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.51,0:09:48.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说回去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.50,0:09:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真大胆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大胆指的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.76,0:09:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊  装纯也要有个限度哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和男生交往过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.05,0:10:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然啦  幼儿园时和同班的隆君…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是之后因为爸爸工作的原因去了国外
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学和初中都没怎么上过  一直是请家教…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.33,0:10:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙难道就是传说中真正的天然吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好烫…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浑身刺痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.49,0:10:31.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凸守的身体就如同伊卡洛斯的翅膀一般被太阳灼伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.14,0:10:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.02,0:10:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么难得的机会  我就帮你搓搓背吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.42,0:10:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好有个不错的丝瓜瓤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.18,0:10:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心… 心领了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.03,0:10:47.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别客气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.65,0:10:49.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:59.20,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fs56\shad0\c&H000000&\b0\frz13.72\fn方正报宋_GBK\pos(286,48)}收件箱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:59.20,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fs56\shad0\c&H000000&\b0\fn方正报宋_GBK\pos(648,72)\frz13.72}富樫勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:59.20,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fs56\shad0\c&H000000&\b0\frz13.72\fn方正报宋_GBK\pos(527,173)}无题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:59.20,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fs56\shad0\c&H000000&\b0\frz11.578\fn方正仿宋_GBK\pos(437,533)}先回去了。\N六花也跟我一起。\N请不用担心。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.94,0:11:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来得还真晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.41,0:11:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太  我进不了房门
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.24,0:11:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密码被修改了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是忘记带钥匙了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.92,0:11:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.94,0:11:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.55,0:11:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.17,0:11:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是管理局的袭击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  不要对我的家人动手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说那么不吉利的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.06,0:11:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.57,0:11:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樟叶和梦叶去林间夏令营了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.94,0:11:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈去上夜班了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.54,0:11:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心一点  这里可能还被伪装过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.58,0:11:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…  大家要明天才回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.92,0:11:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.83,0:11:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚就只有我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.14,0:12:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  厕所在哪边来着…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.91,0:12:22.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枯茗学姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.15,0:12:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一色君也醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:28.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得天黑时的月亮好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以想去散散步来着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.55,0:12:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一色君也一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.14,0:12:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…  等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.33,0:12:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  散步？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去就去呗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我挂了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.82,0:12:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回答也太敷衍人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.06,0:12:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己有了女朋友就不管哥们了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.89,0:12:59.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么时候有女朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.78,0:13:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开学的时候  我帮你创造搭讪机会的大恩你都忘光了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.21,0:13:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我先挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.82,0:13:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要随便打开我的箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.43,0:13:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太  这个是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.49,0:13:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快收起来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.21,0:13:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道这是对我邪王真眼也不能透露的终极装置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.39,0:13:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先这样绑上…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.61,0:13:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能装在这里了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.44,0:13:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后一甩手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.04,0:13:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.06,0:13:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊  勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要热泪盈眶好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪王真眼向你致以无尽的敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.58,0:13:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不需要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.26,0:14:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么想吃的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.64,0:14:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过家里也没什么像样的材料了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.47,0:14:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做不出像十花小姐那样的大手笔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.02,0:14:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其吃这个  我宁愿空手打最终BOSS
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.26,0:14:15.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真坚定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么要去便利店吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟都这么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便利店？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道要吃便利商店里卖的食物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.51,0:14:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  你不喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.95,0:14:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣料理人不准我吃那里的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.11,0:14:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说我必须吃她做的饭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  你应该谢谢她才对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想吃吃看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.86,0:14:38.16,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.71,0:14:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的想吃这些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前在学校看勇太吃过  所以一直很好奇它的构造
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.04,0:14:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先撕开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.69,0:14:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后分离表皮…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.82,0:14:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拉住两边这样扯一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帅气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.56,0:15:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十花小姐要是看到了会生气的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:15.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  还有炸鸡块
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.05,0:15:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别有风味
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.32,0:15:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.36,0:15:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太的饭团是什么味道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.35,0:15:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想尝尝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.09,0:15:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:27.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.24,0:15:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辣到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.27,0:15:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.57,0:15:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为补偿给你这个好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.69,0:15:39.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色代表危险
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次果然不会上当了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,补给完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.34,0:15:47.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  那么回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.97,0:16:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.46,0:16:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还不想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去沐浴一下月光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.95,0:16:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.57,0:16:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:29.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在可是晚上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.61,0:16:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人独处哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.04,0:16:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓的「万事俱备只欠告白」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样啊  你也太薄情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.60,0:16:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我开学时好心和你搭话的恩情都忘光了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.37,0:16:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.09,0:16:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挂了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.82,0:16:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  请您等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.73,0:16:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.83,0:16:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和小鸟游同学怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.34,0:16:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚吃完饭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙忘带家里的钥匙了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.77,0:16:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  该不会也是两人独处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.55,0:16:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就觉得你们两个很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.24,0:17:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到发展这么迅速
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在误会什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种剧情根本不可能发生啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.39,0:17:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.76,0:17:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还问为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.10,0:17:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是六花哦  中二病全开的六花哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.78,0:17:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也是高中生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.13,0:17:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.18,0:17:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.12,0:17:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.28,0:17:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.88,0:17:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.01,0:17:31.51,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fs48\shad0\c&H000000&\b0\frz11.578\fn方正稚艺_GBK\pos(477,284)}你的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.01,0:17:31.51,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fs48\shad0\c&H000000&\b0\frz11.578\fn方正稚艺_GBK\pos(504,373)}好像要讲很久
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.01,0:17:31.51,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fs48\shad0\c&H000000&\b0\frz11.578\fn方正稚艺_GBK\pos(516,472)}我就先回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.01,0:17:31.51,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fs48\shad0\c&H000000&\b0\frz11.578\fn方正稚艺_GBK\pos(739,623)}枯茗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.69,0:17:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和六花…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.53,0:17:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会不会不会  不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.22,0:17:47.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说了  那个满脑子中二的六花根本就没有恋爱的念头吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.47,0:17:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太  这是雷霆战锤之衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.34,0:17:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别甩了  会把衣服撑大的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.06,0:17:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把袖子挽起来不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.62,0:18:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的想象力还真丰富啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.19,0:18:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  已经很晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就睡这个房间吧  赶紧去刷牙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.01,0:18:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有勇太的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.31,0:18:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闻了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.06,0:18:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有勇太的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  感觉好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那关灯了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.66,0:18:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑夜正是邪王真眼状态全满的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.62,0:18:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.06,0:18:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.82,0:18:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.86,0:18:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么我的味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.19,0:18:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说了让你睡觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:18:59.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉心神不宁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.81,0:19:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕它们已经来到这附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.96,0:19:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要加强戒备
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.86,0:19:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.30,0:19:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我关了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心神不宁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡着了就没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心砰砰地跳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.39,0:19:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在给主题公园做广告吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要爆发啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.32,0:19:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.65,0:19:24.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.84,0:19:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  快去睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.35,0:19:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.72,0:19:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.25,0:19:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧  这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.23,0:19:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太  闭上眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.76,0:19:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微一下  稍微一下就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.60,0:19:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙 真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.14,0:20:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说  这样真的好吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.06,0:20:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  等一下…  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.30,0:20:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对效力魔法碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.62,0:20:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是刚才新缔结的契约之印
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.25,0:20:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别画在这么显眼的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.93,0:20:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里最合适
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.84,0:20:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来黑暗之力也会加倍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&HFF}\Naaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa{\alpha}Dark Buster\N从而能施放出比「黑暗火焰」更为强力的「黑暗破坏者」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.49,0:20:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.22,0:20:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中二病到哪都是中二病啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.47,0:20:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样也好…  吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.36,0:21:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心砰砰地跳…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.50,0:21:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.22,0:21:19.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.03,0:21:59.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇太
